Package: ggbilly
Type: Package
Title: Make ggplot2 Easier and Prettier, While Building Intuition For ggplot2
Version: 0.1.0
Author: David Hodge
Maintainer: David Hodge <davidhodge931@gmail.com>
Description: Build beautiful ggplots with ease. Focussed around the gg_blank 
    function, but with various other shortcut functions available. Attempting to 
    align with ggplot2 as much as possible, so users build intuition and
    expertise in how the grammar of graphics works. 
